      "cooked": "<p>Tani ka robote me formen njerezore qe jane ne gjendje te ngasin makinat dhe te kryjne shume nga levjzjet e trupit njerezor. Kjo kronike e euronews tregon avancimet e fundit ne teknologjine robotike, e cila po arrin te zevendesoje njerezit me makinat inteligjente ne disa nga operacionet e shpetimit ne raste zjarri.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"http://www.euronews.com/next/2016/10/24/humanoid-robots-to-replace-search-and-rescue-workers\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/8/6/8657432aa8fa661c5c6d2bfbe8ce0c5ebebb6b7e.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"http://www.euronews.com/next/2016/10/24/humanoid-robots-to-replace-search-and-rescue-workers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"12:49PM - 24 October 2016\">euronews – 24 Oct 16</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/450;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/e/e/eeacc978aa071aa4c12b5433f1ff0b60b20bf236_2_800x450.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/e/e/eeacc978aa071aa4c12b5433f1ff0b60b20bf236_2_800x450.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/e/e/eeacc978aa071aa4c12b5433f1ff0b60b20bf236.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/e/e/eeacc978aa071aa4c12b5433f1ff0b60b20bf236.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/3X/e/e/eeacc978aa071aa4c12b5433f1ff0b60b20bf236_2_10x10.png\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.euronews.com/next/2016/10/24/humanoid-robots-to-replace-search-and-rescue-workers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Humanoid robots to 'replace' search and rescue workers</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Italian researchers are developing a humanoid robot to replace humans in search and rescue operations following disasters.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
